Logo working files

The final files are elsewhere

FOE.Logo.png - original logo png

foe-logo-rect.png - rectangular logo cropped to display on header lne of app
magick FOE.logo.png -trim foe-logo-rect.png

icons/foe-icon512.png  - full size icon
magick FOE.Logo.png resize 580x580 -background white -gravity center -extent 512x512 foe-icon-512.png

icons/foe-icon192.png -  small starter icon
magick foe-icon-512.png -resize 192x192 foe-icon-192.png

